{"tid":1085480,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"★Apple已入殮！蘋果 A7 到 A12X 處理器的首席架構師離職！","createTime":"2019-03-31T07:29:28.000Z","updateTime":"2019-03-31T23:32:38.000Z","uid":19454,"like":18,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"052409e4c6ed18c75daeea3665face76e1f0c140","tid":1085480,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-31T07:29:28.000Z","msg":"今天，CNET 報導帶領蘋果開發 A 系列處理器的首席架構師 Gerard Williams III 已離職。離職前他在蘋果出任平台架構部的高級總裁。<br />\n<br />\nWilliams 在蘋果任職 9 年，從第一顆 64-Bit A7 處理器到 A12X 處理器也由他帶領的開發小組進行研發。在蘋果工作前，他在 ARM 工作了 12 年。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n而他也不是第一位離職的部門高層，其實在 2017 年，當時蘋果的首席架構師 Manu Gulati 被 Google 聘用，因此才交由 William 出任此職位。在位期間，蘋果超過60 項專利申請文件出現了其名字，可見其重要性。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.newmobilelife.com/2019/03/30/a12-gerard-williams-ii-leave-apple/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.newmobilelife.com%2F2019%2F03%2F30%2Fa12-gerard-williams-ii-leave-apple%2F&d=Sk6y7wLkZ8LsH37jlkaP91cETUAZGKrTpJw0Ojiq68w%3D&h=46a78e00\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.newmobilelife.com/2019/03/30/a12-gerard-williams-ii-leave-apple/</a>"},{"pid":"0607271ce9b69081ac5a38513200eaa6600f006a","tid":1085480,"uid":19454,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-31T07:29:50.000Z","msg":"no idevice  anymore<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9c7ea1315eaa53a564441fc351fbac4669e2903b","tid":1085480,"uid":19454,"like":2,"dislike":2,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-31T07:30:21.000Z","msg":"江郎才盡<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1a1e0361252db984ce306b2006fb0680cc800577","tid":1085480,"uid":116688,"like":5,"dislike":4,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-31T07:34:15.000Z","msg":"唔怕啦，出懷舊版iPhone 加價幾千都大把香港人科水喎"},{"pid":"273c175a0b35c73476de7658da3c26b8ec5aae0f","tid":1085480,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-31T12:06:42.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/h